  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he and I answer, where is that, and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But apparently, that was in pipe-- pipes, in the-- you know, in the hotel, piping or plumbing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They're also called-- there is this known effect.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There is this air backup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So sometimes those pipes, they are making noise.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Apparently, there was nobody banging our doors, but there was the pipes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, the next few days we-- we were looking for-- for occupation, for somewhere to work, because you cannot in Vienna to-- to be without work.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this Polish man told us, because he was working there, too, that there is a company, this construction company of engineer Edward Meyer who had [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] such a-- not a factory, works in-- in a 24th [INAUDIBLE], Vienna, which were-- and they were doing their bridges and such steel works.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he gave us address and names and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went to that engineer, Meyer, and he received me, and I asked to work for him.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And his-- his question, first question was, do I know static?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, of course, I know static.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I learned in this [INAUDIBLE] school in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So he gave me a problem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, OK.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sit down here, and do the calculation how you will do the-- a small bridge over a-- a-- some ditch or something like that.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he gave me some-- some data for it and a special book with the steel profiles.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and he said, solve this problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fortunately, I knew how to do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I draw the Cremona diagram, and I calculated the forces and so on, and I looked in the book, and I find out that this proffer will be good for to carry this load and so on.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
